                        <p class="technical-sub-bullet mb-0"><strong>Motor-Driven Fan:</strong> For the condenser cooling air flow.</p>
                        <p class="technical-sub-bullet mb-0"><strong>Automatic Discharge of Condensate:</strong> Drain removes maximum condensate from the system. Microprocessor based controller for controlling solenoid valve timing.</p>
                        <p class="technical-sub-bullet mb-0"><strong>Air-Air Exchanger:</strong> With high thermal performance and low pressure drop.</p>
                        <p class="technical-sub-bullet mb-0"><strong>Hot Gas Bypass Valve:</strong> Controls the refrigerant capacity under all load conditions.</p>
